<template>
  <v-layout
    wrap 
    style="height: 200px;"
  >
    <v-container>
      <v-layout justify-center>
     <v-toolbar-side-icon  @click.stop="drawer = !drawer"></v-toolbar-side-icon>
      </v-layout>
    </v-container>

    <v-navigation-drawer
      v-model="drawer"
      absolute
      temporary
      right
    >
     <v-list class="pa-1">
          <v-list-tile>        
            <v-list-tile-content>
              <v-list-tile-title>ALLB</v-list-tile-title>
            </v-list-tile-content>
          </v-list-tile>
        </v-list>
      <v-list class="pt-0" dense>
        <v-divider></v-divider>
        <v-list-tile
          v-for="item in items"
          :key="item.title"
        >
          <v-list-tile-content>
            <v-list-tile-title>{{ item.title }}</v-list-tile-title>
          </v-list-tile-content>
        </v-list-tile>
      </v-list>
    </v-navigation-drawer>
  </v-layout>
</template>

<script>
  export default {
    data () {
      return {
        drawer: null,
        items: [
          { title: 'Home', icon: 'dashboard' },
          { title: 'About', icon: 'question_answer' }
        ]
      }
    }
  }
</script>

<style>
</style>
